 Latest was a 13th level  cleric in WC. He say &quot;have some items for me plz&quot;, I politely reply &quot;no, but I have some advice for you, go kill some orcs for some cash and exp.&quot; He say &quot; orcs don't have good exp.&quot; I say 'well, I do not give to people who beg from me' He says, &quot;I am not a beggar, I have my own money but I always ask for items from high level people&quot; I left it at that.<br>
 A level 1 halfling druid was begging from me in RV same day earlier. I try to be anon when I go to newbie areas, but this guy started begging from me and when i told him no he started inspecting me. So I moved and he followed me around town and everytime i stopped to do whatever i was doing he would inspect me again. The whole time asking me for money. Finally had enough and ported out. <br>
 <br>
Bleza<br>
